      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This A80 chassis features the legendary 2JZ-GTE power plant, delivering linear power through its factory sequential twin-turbo setup. Mated to a robust Getrag V160 6-speed manual transmission, the drivetrain remains tight with crisp gear engagement. The suspension geometry retains its factory precision, utilizing a double-wishbone configuration for superior lateral grip. Recent maintenance includes a comprehensive timing belt service and refreshing of the vacuum lines to ensure peak boost response. An excellent example for the purist seeking mechanical excellence and a visceral driving experience.",
